<plot>Composed exclusively from the footage of real-life cold calls, Sell It to the Hedge Funds follows ace phone salesman Haven Pell on a cold caller's mission impossible: persuading titans of finance to schedule time for a sales pitch. Comedy, drama and tutorial all intermingle in this highly stylized, fast-paced four minute film.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?485385</url></doc>
